com.aylanetworks.aylasdk.lan

类 LanCommand

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.aylanetworks.aylasdk.lan.LanCommand
  • 直接已知子类:
    AylaLanCommand, CreateDatapointCommand, DeleteSessionCommand, StartScanCommand

    public abstract class LanCommand
extends java.lang.Object
    Represents a LAN command sent to the device. LAN commands are queued by the AylaLanModule for the device, and are returned via responses to requests for commands from the device.

    • 方法详细资料

      • getPayload

        public abstract java.lang.String getPayload()
        Returns the cleartext payload for the LAN command. The response body is a JSON string containing the command data in the format appropriate for the specific command. This method must be overridden by implementers to return the JSON payload of the LAN command.
        返回:
        Unencrypted response JSON for this command.

      • expectsModuleRequest

        public boolean expectsModuleRequest()
        Returns true if the command expects to receive a request from the module as a result of this command. Some commands, such as the CreateDatapointCommand, do not expect an additional request from the module after delivering the command payload, and will return false from this method instead.
        返回:
        true if the command expects to receive a request from the module, false otherwise

      • needsAck

        public boolean needsAck()
        The CreateDatapointCommand is currently the only command that expects an ack to be received after the command has been delivered, and only if the property being updated is configured to be ack-enabled
        返回:
        true if this command needs to wait for an ack from the module before returning success

      • setModuleResponse

        public void setModuleResponse(java.lang.String response)
        Sets the response for this command and notifies waiters that we have been processed
        参数:
        response - Response from the module

      • getModuleResponse

        public java.lang.String getModuleResponse()
        Returns the response text from the module, if received
        返回:
        the module's response string, or null if a response was not received

      • setModuleError

        public void setModuleError(AylaError error)

      • setErrorResponse

        public void setErrorResponse(AylaError error)
        Sets an error response for this command and notifies waiters that we have been processed
        参数:
        error - Error encountered while trying to service this command

      • getResponseError

        public AylaError getResponseError()
        Returns the error from the module, if received
        返回:
        the module's returned error, or null if an error was not received

      • receivedResponse

        public boolean receivedResponse()
        Returns true if this command has received a response from the device. The response may be an error or a string, retreived by getResponseError() or getModuleResponse().
        返回:
        True if this command has received a response

      • getRequestTimeout

        public int getRequestTimeout()
        Returns the timeout in milliseconds for this command.
        返回:
        Timeout for this command in milliseconds

      • setRequestTimeout

        public void setRequestTimeout(int timeout)
        Sets the timeout in milliseconds for this command.
        参数:
        timeout - Time in milliseconds we will wait for this command to complete
